but in three to five minutes,

01:55.616 --> 01:58.285
it weighs
a whopping 30 pounds.

01:58.285 --> 01:58.785
What?!

01:58.785 --> 02:00.554
The best thing
about the StormBag

02:00.554 --> 02:02.589
